---
layout: base.njk
title: Bookmarks | Fahd Ashour
description: Things that caught my interest that I think you would like too.
---

<main class="bookmarks-page">
  <header class="bookmarks-header">
    <h1>Bookmarks</h1>
    <p>things that caught my interest that i think you would like too. Things I recommend you to read.</p>
  </header>

  <section aria-label="bookmarks">
    <div class="bookmarks-list">
      {% for bookmark in bookmarks %}
      <a href="{{ bookmark.url }}" class="bookmark-item" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <span class="bookmark-title">{{ bookmark.title }}</span>
        <span class="bookmark-url">{{ bookmark.url }}</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
